{"tid":2080760,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔福臨門晚餐","createTime":"2020-06-26T15:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T15:15:35.000Z","uid":155005,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"27ea3a0abe2efba1954fb122c649af5e9cc84ed7","tid":2080760,"uid":155005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"今日去冇乜客，可能係平日，我食嗰陣2樓得3-4台，環境好靜，適合同屋企人或者長輩一齊食。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1EvODNF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1EvODNF.png&h=5e6c46a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQGuoeC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQGuoeC.png&h=c87771cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個八寶鴨要預訂，鴨肉夠淋，無呀阿婆都可以食到，裏面有薏米栗子 ，個芡幾正，索晒所有材料d精華。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YeUzzmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYeUzzmP.png&h=13964659&s={SIZE}\" />（9/10）<br />\n<br />\n中式牛柳 -牛肉香，肉味濃，有口感，唔會用鬆肉粉喇得太犀利 炒得夠獲氣[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/5Q3pcrF.png[/img］8/10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Q3pcrF.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD8%2F10&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=e11edc18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/5Q3pcrF.png[/img］8/10</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳皮牛肉餅-呢個係幾香陳皮味，但唔太識欣賞，冇咩特別 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6oj7UFx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6oj7UFx.png&h=1c80dbfd&s={SIZE}\" />6/10<br />\n<br />\n炸子雞-呢個正皮脆內嫩，我建議點檸檬汁食，酸酸咸咸感覺好開胃，食多幾舊都ok 。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfvZLNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmfvZLNC.png&h=d9b01d36&s={SIZE}\" />9/10<br />\n<br />\n梅菜扣肉煲-味道偏甜 ，5花肉係半肥瘦，送飯一流，不過食多舊會覺得膩<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rUDgUO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rUDgUO.png&h=fd585ccb&s={SIZE}\" />8/10<br />\n<br />\n甜品同菜我覺得正常發揮，冇咩要值得評。埋單6個人3300 ，價錢唔算太貴，可以接受。不過有d小菜試過一次下次可以唔洗再試，。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOOwBVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOOwBVj.png&h=2755ff64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nkb9718.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNkb9718.png&h=3938f95c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5xdQfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5xdQfG.png&h=b864d615&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4b618079143415ccf0354d1a6839346fb682a26","tid":2080760,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14763a94d8d371cbd9a48f7f21254eb2cd48ee06","tid":2080760,"uid":2377,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"好撚肚餓呀屌你老母閪"},{"pid":"e078f7255b4df5561d5f9a43fcbfd2b9939829fa","tid":2080760,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"善心打破 0 負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c464e978eaf725d3eb12ed1f405dbcd5f7d0cd","tid":2080760,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"留名等印仔入嚟"},{"pid":"61d72fafeed3b624648ab46b7dcc75551985e364","tid":2080760,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"個扣肉好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c049b098abd34bf3fa282e7591e4404391d80c","tid":2080760,"uid":261524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d5bd6a395a